@parties
go-to: menu

{!<span class="party-dem">Democratic Party</span>!} - The governing coalition party in this scenario. Its internal wings include New Deal liberals, conservative Democrats, labor Democrats, and Southern Democrats.

{!<span class="party-fl">Farmer-Labor</span>!} - A labor-populist and agrarian reform bloc that can support relief, farm debt action, and public works when relations are strong.

Current relations: [+ z_relation : relationships +]

{!<span class="party-liberty">Liberty League</span>!} - Conservative anti-New Deal Democrats, business liberals, and allied independents open to selective cooperation on stabilization policy.

Current relations: [+ ddp_relation : relationships +]

{!<span class="party-gop">Republican Party</span>!} - Cautious reform Republicans and old guard conservatives. They can bargain under pressure, but resist broad structural change.

Current relations: [+ dvp_relation : relationships +]

{!<span class="party-spa">Socialist Party of America</span>!} - Socialist alignment led by Norman Thomas. Potential tactical cooperation depends on Democratic leftward shifts and conference outcomes.

Current relations: [+ kpd_relation : relationships +]

[? if sapd_formed: Left splinter alignment - minor socialist breakaway currents between the Democratic Party and Socialist Party of America. ?]

{!<span class="party-nusj">National Union for Social Justice</span>!} - Father Coughlin-aligned national-populist right. Not available for cooperative coalition governance with Democratic-led governments.

Current relations: [+ dnvp_relation : relationships +]

{!<span class="party-silver">Silver Legion</span>!} - William Pelley-aligned extremist far right. It uses the old NSDAP-backed mechanics internally, but appears as Silver Legion in the U.S. scenario.

Current relations: [+ nsdap_relation : relationships +]

**Other parties** - smaller regional and issue parties with mixed ideological profiles; often decisive in close legislative arithmetic.

Internal source mapping: Democratic Party = SPD, Socialist Party of America = KPD, Farmer-Labor = Z, Liberty League = DDP, Republican Party = DVP, National Union for Social Justice = DNVP, Silver Legion = NSDAP.

